rected recruitment/training/staff development initiatives to maximize productivity and revenue potential through development of a sales team.&nbsp;</li>\\n  <li>Successfully increased employee retention by creating a positive work environment in 18 stores.&nbsp;</li>\\n  <li>Administered daily operations to ensure policies were adhered to and understood by sales staff.</li>\\n  <li>&nbsp;Cultivated strong business relationships with customers to drive business developments.&nbsp;</li>\\n  <li>Planned and executed floor merchandising initiatives in collaboration with merchandise management.&nbsp;</li>\\n  <li>Ensure store is prepared for internal audits through analysis/preparation of quality assurance and Inventory statistics.</li>\\n</ul>","dateTimeValue":"","isValid":true,"errorMessage":""}],"topPadding":0},{"id":"d7533686-f260-ba36-1ef4-823e4a95f9c8","sectionID":"106767ef-9f26-4772-aa69-49692b236bad","index":1,"paragraphTemplateCD":"","docDatas":[{"id":"4a96dc44-9af0-4459-3504-e4307f0013b9","paragraphID":"d7533686-f260-ba36-1ef4-823e4a95f9c8","fieldCD":"JSTD","userId":"128b64b5-b675-404b-bdab-0ab0298ba090","charValue":"8 2012","dateTimeValue":"1997-08-04T18:30:00.000Z","isValid":true,"errorMessage":""},{"id":"efa513a8-f9b3-5a2f-f03b-33d541e44ada","paragraphID":"d7533686-f260-ba36-1ef4-823e4a95f9c8","fieldCD":"EDDT","userId":"128b64b5-b675-404b-bdab-0ab0298ba090","charValue":"8 2015","dateTimeValue":"2009-09-04T18:30:00.000Z","isValid":true,"errorMessage":""},{"id":"c5aae73a-6be8-d0ed-0f73-4cb6747d079e","paragraphID":"d7533686-f260-ba36-1ef4-823e4a95f9c8","fieldCD":"COMP","userId":"128b64b5-b675-404b-bdab-0ab0298ba090","charValue":"Walgreens, Inc ","dateTimeValue":"","isValid":true,"errorMessage":""},{"id":"9faecc94-e74f-2f53-eed7-4b22fa555c76","paragraphID":"d7533686-f260-ba36-1ef4-823e4a95f9c8","fieldCD":"JTIT","userId":"128b64b5-b675-404b-bdab-0ab0298ba090","charValue":"Operations Manager ","dateTimeValue":"","isValid":true,"errorMessage":""},{"id":"edeb2a4d-af